{{!-- Finale — "The algorithm doesn't owe us anything." Full-width muted video
     with the quote and one big Subscribe button that opens the pitch modal
     (#subscribe-backdrop, defined in the navbar). Follows every theme mode. --}}
<section class="reveal tv-scanlines relative mt-16 flex min-h-[70vh] items-center overflow-hidden" id="home-subscribe" style="background:#08080a">
	<div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden" aria-hidden="true">
		<iframe
			src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/ecOkmTD7KhU?autoplay=1&amp;mute=1&amp;loop=1&amp;controls=0&amp;playlist=ecOkmTD7KhU&amp;playsinline=1&amp;rel=0&amp;modestbranding=1&amp;iv_load_policy=3&amp;disablekb=1"
			title="Ambient background video"
			tabindex="-1"
			loading="lazy"
			allow="autoplay; encrypted-media"
			style="position:absolute; top:50%; left:50%; width:100vw; height:56.25vw; min-height:100%; min-width:calc(100vh * 1.7778); transform:translate(-50%,-50%) scale(1.12); border:0; pointer-events:none;"></iframe>
		<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/70"></div>
	</div>

	<div class="container-site relative py-20 text-center text-white">
		<p class="mx-auto inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-white/20 bg-white/10 px-4 py-1.5 font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] backdrop-blur animate-fade-in">{{> "icons/bell" class="h-3.5 w-3.5"}} own your feed</p>
		<blockquote class="mx-auto mt-7 max-w-3xl text-3xl font-bold leading-tight tracking-tight text-balance sm:text-5xl [text-shadow:0_2px_16px_rgb(0_0_0/.5)]">
			"The algorithm doesn't owe us anything."
		</blockquote>
		<p class="mx-auto mt-5 max-w-xl text-base leading-relaxed text-white/75 sm:text-lg">If YouTube shut down tomorrow, we'd lose each other. This site is the one place we actually own — subscribe here and no recommendation engine can come between us.</p>
		<button type="button" class="btn mx-auto mt-9 !bg-white !px-8 !py-3.5 !text-base !font-bold !text-black shadow-lift transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:opacity-95" data-modal-open="#subscribe-backdrop">
			{{> "icons/bell" class="h-4 w-4"}} Subscribe — it's free
		</button>
		<p class="mt-4 font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-white/50">email only · ads off for members · unsubscribe anytime</p>
	</div>
</section>
